title: Ebro In The Morning - SUMMER JAM IS BACK
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning.

In this episode, Ebro talks about the NY Grand Jury & Trump's case (7:20), Rosenberg talks about the recent John Cena-Taiwan scandal (11:40), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (31:00 & 58:00). 

Did we mention that SUMMER JAM IS BACK? (30 minutes)
